OL,3,CDoctor cleared of killing patient
OL,5,FA doctor has been acquitted of the
OL,6,Fmanslaughter of a female patient who
OL,7,Fdied in a care home in Londonderry
OL,8,Feight years ago.
OL,10,FIvan Pepelyashkov was due to stand
OL,11,Ftrial on a charge of unlawfully
OL,12,Fkilling Michele McGuigan on May 13,
OL,13,F2018.
OL,15,FThe 48-year old, from Riverside in
OL,16,FAntrim, had denied the charge and he
OL,17,Fappeared at Belfast Crown Court today.
