OL,3,CDoctor cleared of killing patient
OL,5,FAfter eight men and four women were
OL,6,Fsworn to serve as a jury, Madam
OL,7,FJustice McBride was addressed by Crown
OL,8,Fbarrister Frank O'Donoghoe KC.
OL,10,FHe said that after taking instructions
OL,11,Ffrom the Director of Public
OL,12,FProsecutions, the Crown would not be
OL,13,Foffered any evidence against Dr
OL,14,FPepelyashkov.
OL,16,FMadam Justice McBride then spoke to
OL,17,Fthe 12 jurors and instructed the
OL,18,Fforeman to enter a plea of 'not guilty
OL,19,Fby direction.'
