OL,3,CDoctor cleared of killing patient
OL,5,FFollowing this, Mr O'Donoghoe revealed
OL,6,Fthere was "nothing further" against
OL,7,Fthe doctor.
OL,9,FThe senior Judge then addressed the
OL,10,FBulgarian-born doctor in the dock and
OL,11,Ftold him: "You have been found not
OL,12,Fguilty on the direction of the jury
OL,13,Fand you are therefore free to go."
OL,15,FDespite no details being aired today,
OL,16,Fit is understood that the charge
OL,17,Frelated to an incident in the Owen Mor
OL,18,FCare Centre on Derry's Culmore Road.
