OL,3,CDoctor cleared of killing patient
OL,5,FA second defendant, Easteden Limited
OL,6,Fwhich is based on Erganagh Road in
OL,7,FOmagh, has also been charged with an
OL,8,Foffence arising from the incident.
OL,10,FThe company, which owns the care home,
OL,11,Fhas been charged with a health and
OL,12,Fsafety breach - namely that on a date
OL,13,Fbetween May 10 and 14, 2018 it failed
OL,14,Fto ensure the safety of a non-employee.
OL,16,FEasteden Limited has denied the charge
OL,17,Fand a trial will be held at a later
OL,18,Fdate.
